      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "For sale is a preserved 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition, featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been professionally bulletproofed. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is flawless, with proactive subframe reinforcement and recent rod bearing replacement documented. The suspension geometry remains tight, upgraded with Bilstein B16 dampers for superior damping control without compromising the original MacPherson/multi-link kinematics. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the aesthetic matches the mechanical excellence. No deferred maintenance; this is a turn-key collector-grade example for the true driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
